2.  **Install C++ dependencies (if not using system-wide packages or Conan):**
    The `CMakeLists.txt` assumes `nlohmann/json`, `spdlog`, and `jwt-cpp` are either vendored in `src/deps` or available system-wide. For this project, they are set up to be cloned into `src/deps` by the Dockerfile. For local development, you might need to manually clone them: